<div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="title"><h1>WELCOME TO CLOUDSPOKES</h1></div>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span6">
            <p><br/>CloudSpokes is a unique developer community, focused on using APIs, mobile technologies and public cloud platforms to build and deliver enterprise class solutions! Compete in development challenges for cash, prizes and bragging rights and learn new skills. <a href="#register-modal" data-toggle="modal">Register to get started</a> or <a href="/how-it-works-members">see how the process works.</a></p>

            <p><a class="btn" href="#register-modal" data-toggle="modal"><span>Register to get started</span></a></p>

